  m_text: "B\xF6lgedeki mahalle \u015Fenli\u011Finden bir vatanda\u015Ftan yang\u0131n
    ihbar\u0131 al\u0131nd\u0131. Arayan ki\u015Fi durumu \u015F\xF6yle aktar\u0131yor:
    \"Etkinlik alan\u0131nda \u0131zgaralardan birinde ya\u011F yang\u0131n\u0131
    \xE7\u0131kt\u0131! Di\u011Fer \u0131zgaralar normal yan\u0131yor ama bu tamamen
    kontrolden \xE7\u0131kt\u0131. Alevleri \xE7ok daha y\xFCksek ve etrafa \xE7ok
    yo\u011Fun duman yay\u0131yor.\" B\xF6lgeye ilk m\xFCdahale bekleniyor."
